    There are skills like Mining, Woodcutting, Crafting, and more.
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Each skill serves its own purpose, use the rocks mined to smith stronger gear, and increase your
    <strong>
     max hit
    </strong>
    .
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
